HEADWORD: freewheeling
<hw>freewheeling</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Acting heedless of
consequences; acting without controls, external or internal; <as>as,
<ex>freewheeling</ex> foolishness</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> careless, irresponsible, reckless.</syn>⟦br⟧
